<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2007-06-15</DATELINE><TITLE>On fractional order differential equations model for nonlocal epidemics</TITLE><BODY>Abstract A fractional order model for nonlocal epidemics is given. Stability of fractional order equations is studied. The results are expected to be relevant to foot-and-mouth disease, SARS and avian flu.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>